999/*



1000 * Initialize rtNaN needed by the generated code.



1001 * NaN is initialized as non-signaling. Assumes IEEE.



1002 */



1003real_T rtGetNaN(void)



1004{



1005  size_t bitsPerReal = sizeof(real_T) * (NumBitsPerChar);



1006  real_T nan = 0.0;



1007  if (bitsPerReal == 32U) {



1008    nan = rtGetNaNF();



1009  } else {



1010    union {



1011      LittleEndianIEEEDouble bitVal;



1012      real_T fltVal;



1013    } tmpVal;



1014



1015    tmpVal.bitVal.words.wordH = 0xFFF80000U;



1016    tmpVal.bitVal.words.wordL = 0x00000000U;



1017    nan = tmpVal.fltVal;



1018  }



1019



1020  return nan;



1021}

1032  return nanF.wordL.wordLreal;



1033}

1035/* Detect zero crossings events. */



1036ZCEventType rt_ZCFcn(ZCDirection zcDir, ZCSigState* prevZc, real_T currValue)



1037{



1038  slZcEventType zcsDir;



1039  slZcEventType tempEv;



1040  ZCEventType zcEvent = NO_ZCEVENT;    /* assume */



1041



1042  /* zcEvent matrix */



1043  static const slZcEventType eventMatrix[4][4] = {



1044    /*          ZER              POS              NEG              UNK */



1045    { SL_ZCS_EVENT_NUL, SL_ZCS_EVENT_Z2P, SL_ZCS_EVENT_Z2N, SL_ZCS_EVENT_NUL },/* ZER */



1046



1047    { SL_ZCS_EVENT_P2Z, SL_ZCS_EVENT_NUL, SL_ZCS_EVENT_P2N, SL_ZCS_EVENT_NUL },/* POS */



1048



1049    { SL_ZCS_EVENT_N2Z, SL_ZCS_EVENT_N2P, SL_ZCS_EVENT_NUL, SL_ZCS_EVENT_NUL },/* NEG */



1050



1051    { SL_ZCS_EVENT_NUL, SL_ZCS_EVENT_NUL, SL_ZCS_EVENT_NUL, SL_ZCS_EVENT_NUL }/* UNK */



1052  };



1053



1054  /* get prevZcEvent and prevZcSign from prevZc */



1055  slZcEventType prevEv = (slZcEventType)(((uint8_T)(*prevZc)) >> 2);



1056  slZcSignalSignType prevSign = (slZcSignalSignType)(((uint8_T)(*prevZc)) &



1057    (uint8_T)0x03);



1058



1059  /* get current zcSignal sign from current zcSignal value */



1060  slZcSignalSignType currSign = (slZcSignalSignType)((currValue) > 0.0 ?



1061    SL_ZCS_SIGN_POS :



1062    ((currValue) < 0.0 ? SL_ZCS_SIGN_NEG : SL_ZCS_SIGN_ZERO));



1063



1064  /* get current zcEvent based on prev and current zcSignal value */



1065  slZcEventType currEv = eventMatrix[prevSign][currSign];



1066



1067  /* get slZcEventType from ZCDirection */



1068  switch (zcDir) {



1069   case ANY_ZERO_CROSSING:



1070    zcsDir = SL_ZCS_EVENT_ALL;



1071    break;



1072



1073   case FALLING_ZERO_CROSSING:



1074    zcsDir = SL_ZCS_EVENT_ALL_DN;



1075    break;



1076



1077   case RISING_ZERO_CROSSING:



1078    zcsDir = SL_ZCS_EVENT_ALL_UP;



1079    break;



1080



1081   default:



1082    zcsDir = SL_ZCS_EVENT_NUL;



1083    break;



1084  }



1085



1086  /*had event, check if double zc happend remove double detection. */



1087  if (slZcHadEvent(currEv, zcsDir)) {



1088    currEv = (slZcEventType)(slZcUnAliasEvents(prevEv, currEv));



1089  } else {



1090    currEv = SL_ZCS_EVENT_NUL;



1091  }



1092



1093  /* Update prevZc */



1094  tempEv = (slZcEventType)(currEv << 2);/* shift left by 2 bits */



1095  *prevZc = (ZCSigState)((currSign) | (tempEv));



1096  if ((currEv & SL_ZCS_EVENT_ALL_DN) != 0) {



1097    zcEvent = FALLING_ZCEVENT;



1098  } else if ((currEv & SL_ZCS_EVENT_ALL_UP) != 0) {



1099    zcEvent = RISING_ZCEVENT;



1100  } else {



1101    zcEvent = NO_ZCEVENT;



1102  }



1103



1104  return zcEvent;



1105}                                      /* rt_ZCFcn */

1216static uint16_T look1_iu16lu64n48_binlcse(uint16_T u0, const uint16_T bp0[],



1217  const uint16_T table[], uint32_T maxIndex)



1218{



1219  uint16_T y;



1220  uint64_T frac;



1221  uint32_T iRght;



1222  uint32_T iLeft;



1223  uint32_T bpIdx;



1224



1225  /* Lookup 1-D



1226     Search method: 'binary'



1227     Use previous index: 'off'



1228     Interpolation method: 'Linear point-slope'



1229     Extrapolation method: 'Clip'



1230     Use last breakpoint for index at or above upper limit: 'off'



1231     Remove protection against out-of-range input in generated code: 'off'



1232     Rounding mode: 'simplest'



1233   */



1234  /* Prelookup - Index and Fraction



1235     Index Search method: 'binary'



1236     Extrapolation method: 'Clip'



1237     Use previous index: 'off'



1238     Use last breakpoint for index at or above upper limit: 'off'



1239     Remove protection against out-of-range input in generated code: 'off'



1240     Rounding mode: 'simplest'



1241   */



1242  if (u0 <= bp0[0U]) {



1243    iLeft = 0U;



1244    frac = 0ULL;



1245  } else if (u0 < bp0[maxIndex]) {



1246    /* Binary Search */



1247    bpIdx = maxIndex >> 1U;



1248    iLeft = 0U;



1249    iRght = maxIndex;



1250    while (iRght - iLeft > 1U) {



1251      if (u0 < bp0[bpIdx]) {



1252        iRght = bpIdx;



1253      } else {



1254        iLeft = bpIdx;



1255      }



1256



1257      bpIdx = (iRght + iLeft) >> 1U;



1258    }



1259



1260    frac = ((uint64_T)(uint16_T)((uint32_T)u0 - bp0[iLeft]) << 48) / (uint16_T)



1261      ((uint32_T)bp0[iLeft + 1U] - bp0[iLeft]);



1262  } else {



1263    iLeft = maxIndex - 1U;



1264    frac = 281474976710656ULL;



1265  }



1266



1267  /* Interpolation 1-D



1268     Interpolation method: 'Linear point-slope'



1269     Use last breakpoint for index at or above upper limit: 'off'



1270     Rounding mode: 'simplest'



1271     Overflow mode: 'wrapping'



1272   */



1273  if (table[iLeft + 1U] >= table[iLeft]) {



1274    y = (uint16_T)((uint32_T)(uint16_T)(((uint16_T)((uint32_T)table[iLeft + 1U]



1275      - table[iLeft]) * frac) >> 48) + table[iLeft]);



1276  } else {



1277    y = (uint16_T)((uint32_T)table[iLeft] - (uint16_T)(((uint16_T)((uint32_T)



1278      table[iLeft] - table[iLeft + 1U]) * frac) >> 48));



1279  }



1280



1281  return y;



1282}

1340/* Output and update for function-call system: '<S49>/Gearmotor_brake' */

2351   *  y = u * K where K = 1 / ( w * Ts )



2352   */



2353  rtb_TSamp = rtb_SignPreIntegrator / ((real_T)



2354    localDW->MODESACCELERATION_PIDLAUNCH8ACT * 0.001);



2355



2356  /* Delay: '<S116>/UD' */



2357  if (rt_ZCFcn(RISING_ZERO_CROSSING,&localZCE->UD_Reset_ZCE,



2358               (rtu_reset)) != NO_ZCEVENT) {



2359    localDW->UD_DSTATE = 0.0;



2360  }



2361



2362  /* Sum: '<S112>/Sum' incorporates:



2363   *  Delay: '<S116>/UD'



2364   *  Product: '<S112>/POut'



2365   *  Sum: '<S116>/Diff'



2366   */



2367  rtb_SignPreIntegrator = (rtb_IOut * rtb_Saturate + Integrator) + (rtb_TSamp -



2368    localDW->UD_DSTATE);



2369



2370  /* Saturate: '<S112>/Saturate' */



2371  if (rtb_SignPreIntegrator > 20.0) {



2372    rtb_Saturate = 20.0;



2373  } else if (rtb_SignPreIntegrator < -20.0) {



2374    rtb_Saturate = -20.0;



2375  } else {



2376    rtb_Saturate = rtb_SignPreIntegrator;



2377  }



2378



2379  /* End of Saturate: '<S112>/Saturate' */



2380



2381  /* Sum: '<S80>/Sum' incorporates:



2382   *  Constant: '<S80>/Constant1'



2383   */



2384  *rty_clutchVal = 20.0 - rtb_Saturate;



2385



2386  /* Sum: '<S80>/Minus' incorporates:



2387   *  Constant: '<S80>/Constant'



2388   */



2389  localDW->Minus = 100.0 - *rty_clutchVal;



2390



2391  /* S-Function (ClutchMotor_setPWMRegister): '<S80>/ClutchMotor SetPWMRegister' */



2392  ClutchMotor_setPWMRegister_Outputs_wrapper(&localDW->Minus);



2393



2394  /* Gain: '<S115>/ZeroGain' */



2395  rtb_Saturate = 0.0 * rtb_SignPreIntegrator;



2396



2397  /* DeadZone: '<S115>/DeadZone' */



2398  if (rtb_SignPreIntegrator > 20.0) {



2399    rtb_SignPreIntegrator -= 20.0;



2400  } else if (rtb_SignPreIntegrator >= -20.0) {



2401    rtb_SignPreIntegrator = 0.0;



2402  } else {



2403    rtb_SignPreIntegrator -= -20.0;



2404  }



2405



2406  /* End of DeadZone: '<S115>/DeadZone' */



2407



2408  /* RelationalOperator: '<S115>/NotEqual' */



2409  rtb_NotEqual = (rtb_Saturate != rtb_SignPreIntegrator);



2410



2411  /* Signum: '<S115>/SignDeltaU' */



2412  if (rtb_SignPreIntegrator < 0.0) {



2413    rtb_SignPreIntegrator = -1.0;



2414  } else if (rtb_SignPreIntegrator > 0.0) {



2415    rtb_SignPreIntegrator = 1.0;



2416  } else if (rtb_SignPreIntegrator == 0.0) {



2417    rtb_SignPreIntegrator = 0.0;



2418  } else {



2419    rtb_SignPreIntegrator = (rtNaN);



2420  }



2421



2422  /* End of Signum: '<S115>/SignDeltaU' */



2423



2424  /* Product: '<S112>/IOut' incorporates:



2425   *  Constant: '<S80>/Constant14'



2426   */



2427  rtb_IOut *= 10.0;



2428



2429  /* Update for DiscreteIntegrator: '<S112>/Integrator' */



2430  localDW->Integrator_SYSTEM_ENABLE = 0U;



2431  localDW->Integrator_DSTATE = Integrator;



2432  if (rtu_reset > 0.0) {



2433    localDW->Integrator_PrevResetState = 1;



2434  } else if (rtu_reset < 0.0) {



2435    localDW->Integrator_PrevResetState = -1;



2436  } else if (rtu_reset == 0.0) {



2437    localDW->Integrator_PrevResetState = 0;



2438  } else {



2439    localDW->Integrator_PrevResetState = 2;



2440  }



2441



2442  /* DataTypeConversion: '<S115>/DataTypeConv1' */



2443  if (rtb_SignPreIntegrator < 128.0) {



2444    rtb_SignPreIntegrator_d = (int8_T)rtb_SignPreIntegrator;



2445  } else {



2446    rtb_SignPreIntegrator_d = MAX_int8_T;



2447  }



2448



2449  /* End of DataTypeConversion: '<S115>/DataTypeConv1' */



2450



2451  /* Signum: '<S115>/SignPreIntegrator' */



2452  if (rtb_IOut < 0.0) {



2453    rtb_SignPreIntegrator = -1.0;



2454  } else if (rtb_IOut > 0.0) {



2455    rtb_SignPreIntegrator = 1.0;



2456  } else if (rtb_IOut == 0.0) {



2457    rtb_SignPreIntegrator = 0.0;



2458  } else {



2459    rtb_SignPreIntegrator = (rtNaN);



2460  }



2461



2462  /* End of Signum: '<S115>/SignPreIntegrator' */



2463



2464  /* Switch: '<S112>/Switch' incorporates:



2465   *  DataTypeConversion: '<S115>/DataTypeConv2'



2466   *  Logic: '<S115>/AND'



2467   *  RelationalOperator: '<S115>/Equal'



2468   */



2469  if (rtb_NotEqual && (rtb_SignPreIntegrator_d == (int8_T)rtb_SignPreIntegrator))



2470  {



2471    /* Update for DiscreteIntegrator: '<S112>/Integrator' incorporates:



2472     *  Constant: '<S112>/Constant'



2473     */



2474    localDW->Integrator_PREV_U = 0.0;



2475  } else {



2476    /* Update for DiscreteIntegrator: '<S112>/Integrator' */



2477    localDW->Integrator_PREV_U = rtb_IOut;



2478  }



2479



2480  /* End of Switch: '<S112>/Switch' */



2481



2482  /* Update for Delay: '<S116>/UD' */



2483  localDW->UD_DSTATE = rtb_TSamp;



2484}

2494static void NEUTRAL_STATE(void)

2518    }



2519    break;

2521   case IN_UNSET_NEUTRAL:

2525    }



2526    break;

2530/* Function for Chart: '<S5>/GCULogic' */



2531static int32_T Gearshift_getTime(void)



2532{



2533  int32_T time;



2534  if (rtDW.is_UPSHIFTING == IN_UP_START) {



2535    if (rtDW.is_NEUTRAL_STATE == IN_SET_NEUTRAL) {



2536      time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)DEFAULT_NT_CLUTCH_DELAY];



2537    } else {



2538      time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)DELAY];



2539    }



2540  } else if (rtDW.is_UPSHIFTING == IN_UP_PUSH) {



2541    if (rtDW.is_NEUTRAL_STATE == IN_SET_NEUTRAL) {



2542      time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)NT_CLUTCH_DELAY];



2543    } else {



2544      switch (rtDW.RateTransition36[6]) {



2545       case 1:



2546        time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)UP_PUSH_1_2];



2547        break;



2548



2549       case 2:



2550        time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)UP_PUSH_2_3];



2551        break;



2552



2553       case 3:



2554        time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)UP_PUSH_3_4];



2555        break;



2556



2557       case 4:



2558        time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)UP_PUSH_4_5];



2559        break;



2560



2561       default:



2562        time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)UP_PUSH_2_3];



2563        break;



2564      }



2565    }



2566  } else if (rtDW.is_UPSHIFTING == IN_UP_REBOUND) {



2567    if (rtDW.is_NEUTRAL_STATE == IN_SET_NEUTRAL) {



2568      time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)NT_REBOUND_1_N];



2569    } else {



2570      time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)UP_REBOUND];



2571    }



2572  } else if (rtDW.is_UPSHIFTING == IN_UP_BRAKE) {



2573    if (rtDW.is_NEUTRAL_STATE == IN_SET_NEUTRAL) {



2574      time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)NT_BRAKE_1_N];



2575    } else {



2576      time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)UP_BRAKE];



2577    }



2578  } else if (rtDW.is_DOWNSHIFTING == IN_DOWN_START) {



2579    time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)CLUTCH];



2580  } else if (rtDW.is_DOWNSHIFTING == IN_DOWN_PUSH) {



2581    time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)DN_PUSH];



2582  } else if (rtDW.is_DOWNSHIFTING == IN_DOWN_REBOUND) {



2583    time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)DN_REBOUND];



2584  } else {



2585    time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)DN_BRAKE];



2586  }



2587



2588  return time;



2589}
